### Search Policies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/policies?page=0&size=10&keyword=청년
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Matched Policies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/policies/matched
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Check Eligibility
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/policies/1/eligibility
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
